                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="congratulations-expressions-and-responses">
                            1. Congratulations expressions and responses</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>A:yay i finally passed test! </p><p>B. congratulations on passing your test! </p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>semoga membantu dan maaf kalau tidak cocok❤</p> Yay i finally passed 4 gread <br />Congratulesion i am so Happy for you<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="congratulations-expressions-and-responses-create-new-robots-contoh-nya-apa">
                            2. congratulations expressions and responses create new robots contoh nya apa?</h2><br />
                        pujian : "You have done a great job for your robots, congratulations for you"<br />respon : "thank you so much"menanyakan kabar:How are yo today <br />respon : i'm fine thanks you<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="garis-bawahi-lah-kalimat-mana-yang-menggunakan-ucapan-selamat-expressions-congratulations-and-responsestolong-di-bantu-%e2%80%8b">
                            3. garis bawahi lah kalimat mana yang menggunakan ucapan selamat (expressions congratulations and responses)tolong di bantu ​</h2><br />
                        <p>Jawaban: dibawah adalah kalimatnya. semoga membantu </p><p></p><p>Penjelasan:</p><p>Wow, thank you very much for telling me.</p><p>Thank you very much for saying so.</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="write-down-expressions-and-responses-of-polite-expressions%e2%80%8b">
