                            13. examples of apology expressions and responses​</h2><br />
                        <p></p><p>[tex]{\huge{\purple{\mathfrak{ Jawaban :}}}}[/tex]</p><strong>Expression of Apologizing </strong><p></p><p><strong>Sorry</strong> ( maaf ) </p><p><strong>I'm so sorry</strong> ( aku sangat minta maaf ) </p><p><strong>I'm really sorry</strong> ( aku benar-benar minta maaf ) </p><p><strong>I'm terrybly sorry</strong> ( aku sangat minta maaf ) </p><p><strong>Please forgive </strong><strong>me</strong> ( tolong maafkan aku ) </p><p><strong>Please accept my apology</strong> ( tolong terima permintaan maafku ) </p><p>. </p><strong>Responses</strong><strong> </strong><strong>of</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Apologizing</strong><p></p><p><strong>It's fine / It's okay / It's alright</strong> ( tidak apa-apa ) </p><p><strong>that's fine / that's okay / that's alright</strong> ( tidak apa-apa ) </p><p><strong>forget</strong><strong> </strong><strong>it</strong><strong> </strong> ( lupakan saja ) </p><p><strong>don't</strong><strong> </strong><strong>worry</strong><strong> </strong><strong>about</strong><strong> </strong><strong>it</strong><strong> </strong>( jangan khawatir tentang itu ) </p><p><strong>it</strong><strong> </strong><strong>doesn't</strong><strong> </strong><strong>matter</strong><strong> </strong>( itu bukan masalah ) </p><p><strong>don't</strong><strong> </strong><strong>mention</strong><strong> </strong><strong>it</strong><strong> </strong>( tidak apa-apa ) </p><p><strong>never</strong><strong> </strong><strong>mind</strong><strong> </strong>( jangan dipikirkan ) </p><p></p><p>• - - - • - - - • - - - • - - - •</p>Answers Details :<p></p><strong>Subjects : </strong>English<strong>Class : </strong>7 <strong>Subject Matter :</strong><strong> </strong>Chapter 1 -<strong> </strong>Greetings, Leave-takings, 
