                            20. Bantu Jawab...1. write 5 congratulations and their responses2. Write down 5 expressions of agreeing and disagreeing along with their responses (Di terjemahkan juga yah..)[tex]\large{\pink{\boxed{Unrequited Love}}}[/tex]​</h2><br />
                        <p>-Congratulations on your Graduation!</p><p>response: Thank you so much^^!</p><p>-I am very happy for you.</p><p></p><p>response: Thank you. I cannot forget your help</p><p>-Good for you.</p><p></p><p>response: Thank you very much</p><p>-That was wonderful</p><p>response: Thank you so much</p><p>-That was great.</p><p></p><p>response: Thanks. I am glad.</p><p>----------------------------------------------------------------</p><p>-I'm very sorry, but I don't agree with your plan (disagree)</p><p>-That sounds good, we like it (agree)</p><p>-I don't agree with your Idea, it's to risky (disagree)</p><p>-we have no agreement with you (disagree)</p><p>-we really liked your Ideas (agree)</p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>Buat translatenya pake google trans aja:D</strong></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="congratulatig-expressions-and-responses">
                            21. Congratulatig expressions and responses</h2><br />
                        this expresions are used to congratulate someone:<br />-congratulation<br />-well done<br />-well done<br /><br />response:<br />thank you<br />thanks a lot<br />thank you verry much=&gt; Answer :<br />If we want to congratulate someone, we say :<br />1.) Congratulations, ...<br />Example : Congratulations, Lina. You win the competition.<br />2.) Good job, ....<br />Example : Good job, Beni. This floor looks clean now.<br /><br />If we want to response someone's congratulate, we say :<br />1.) Thank you.<br />2.) Thank you so much.<br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Maaf jika salah. Semog membantu ^_^<br /><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="mention-5-expression-of-congratulations-and-the-responses">
                            22. Mention 5 expression of congratulations and the responses!</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>Congratulating expressions:
</p><p>
</p><p>1. Congratulations! You deserved it, man!
</p><p>
</p><p>Response: Thank you very much. Your support means a lot.
</p><p>
</p><p>2. I am very happy for you.
</p><p>
</p><p>Response: Thank you. I cannot forget your help, and I will still need your help.
</p><p>
</p><p>3.That's wonderful.
</p><p>
</p><p>Response: Oh, thanks.
</p><p>
</p><p>4. Good for you.
</p><p>
</p><p>Response: Thank you very much
</p><p>
</p><p>5. Well done.
</p><p>
</p><p>Response: Thank you for saying so.</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>The social purpose of congratulating people is to express our happiness about someone's achievement.
</p><p>
</p><p>When do we congratulate people?
</p><p>
</p><p>We congratulate people when we hear good news about someone's achievement, promotion, graduation, etc.</p><br />
