                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="1-write-some-expressions-of-greeting-and-the-responses-52-write-some-expressions-of-leave-taking-and-the-responses-5%e2%80%8b">
                            28. 1. write some expressions of greeting and the responses (5)2. write some expressions of leave taking and the responses (5)​</h2><br />
                        <p>Here are the answers for those questions above. </p>Expressions of greeting: <strong>How are you doing?   </strong>response<strong>: I'm fine. / Great.</strong><strong>What's up, dude?        </strong>response<strong>: Not much.</strong><strong>Hello there.                 </strong>response:<strong> Hello.</strong><strong>How do you do?         </strong>response<strong>: How do you do?</strong><strong>Good morning           </strong> response:<strong> Good morning / Morning.</strong><p>     2. Expression of leave-taking:</p><strong>See you around, mate.     </strong>response<strong>: See you.</strong><strong>Goodbye.                           </strong>response<strong>: Bye.</strong><strong>I gotta get going now.       </strong>response:<strong> OK, then take care.</strong><strong>Nice to see you.                </strong>response:<strong> Nice to see you too.</strong><strong>Catch you later.                </strong>response: <strong>Sure, see you later/ Later.</strong><p></p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong><p>Expression of greeting adalah ungkapan dalam memulai percakapan atau menyapa seseorang. Lima ungkapan diatas adalah yang paling umum diucapkan dalam percakapan sehari-hari. Satu ungkapan yang paling formal adalah nomor empat, dimana kita hanya mengucapkan 'How do you do?' saat baru pertama kali pertemu seseorang dalam situasi formal. Namun responsnya bukan seperti 'how are you? yaitu 'I'm fine' , tetapi tetap dengan 'How do you do?' . Konsep ini tidak ada dalam bahasa Indonesia. </p><p>Sementara itu expression of leave taking adalah ungkapan dalam mengakhiri pembicaraan atau perpisahan.Lima contoh diatas hanyalah sebagian saja yang paling sering digunakan, terutama dalam situasi informal, seperti contoh pada nomor lima misalnya. Hal itu jamak digunakan dalam percakapan sehari-hari antar teman dekat.</p><p></p>Pelajari lebih lanjut: <p>Materi tentang greeting</p><p>https://brainly.co.id/tugas/6498452</p><p>Materi tentang leave taking</p><p>https://brainly.co.id/tugas/568062</p><p>https://brainly.co.id/tugas/2931524</p><p></p>Detil Jawaban:<p>Kelas: SMP</p><p>Mapel: English</p><p>Bab: Greetings and leave takings</p><p>Kode: 7.5.1</p><p>#TingkatkanPrestasimu #SPJ3</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="cpngratulating-expressions-and-responses">
                            29. Cpngratulating expressions and responses</h2><br />
                        1.a: congratulations for your success<br />b: thanks.<br />2. a: good job! you're so cool, u can do it. bro<br />b: thx bro. i can't do it without u.<br />semoga membantu<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="write-two-responses-when-a-friend-give-you-congratulations-expressions%e2%80%8b">
                            30.  Write two responses when a friend give you congratulations expressions'​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>1. Thank you so much</p><p>2. I appreciate it</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>1. Terima kasih banyak
</p><p>2. Saya menghargainya</p><p><strong></strong></p><strong>Tolong jadikan Brainliest answer / Jawaban terpintar ya.. hehe</strong><p></p><p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>• It's very good of you to say so</p><p>• Thank you, I can't forget your help to me</p><p>• How nice of You to say so</p><p>• Thank you very much for saying so</p><p>• I'm glad you think so</p><p>• Oh, actually it's nothing special</p><p>• Oh, I have a lot to learn yet</p><p>• Oh, not really</p><p>• Oh, nothing to it, actually</p><p>• Oh, thanks</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>gapapa kan lebih dari satu? :v</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="mention-five-expressions-of-greeting-and-its-responses">
                            31. Mention five expressions of greeting and its responses</h2><br />
                        greeting and responses ;<br /><br />- good morning = good morning <br />- good aftenoon= good afternoon <br />- good night = good night <br />- good bay =bay <br /><br />yang aku tahu hanya itu.selengkapnya cari di internet okss <br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="contoh-kalimat-the-expressions-of-wish-and-responses">
                            32. Contoh kalimat the expressions of wish and responses</h2><br />
                        Expression= WIsh you have a good score on the english exam<br />Responses= Thank you so much... i hope that so<br /><br />Semoga Bermanfaat :)<br /><br />the espressions of wish<br />-i hope you will get an A for the English test.<br />-I hope you have a save trip<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="write-5five-expressions-of-hopeswishes5fiveexpressions-of-congratulations-and-their-responsestolong-di-bantu-%e2%80%8b">
                            33. write 5(five) expressions of hopes/wishes,5(five)expressions of congratulations and their responsesTolong di bantu ​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>exp (hope/wish)</p><p>1. I wish to be a superman</p><p>2. I hope some day i could be a doctor</p><p>3. I hope you get well soon </p><p>4. I hope you have a nice day</p><p>5. I wish that my parents wealthy</p><p>exp (congrats)</p><p>1. congrats on your wedding!</p><p>2. congrats for you!</p><p>3. congrats for a son!</p><p>4. congrats on your graduation!</p><p>5. congrats that you got promoted!</p><p></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="task-5complete-the-following-table-with-the-expressions-of-congratulationsand-the-responses-you-find-in-the-preceding-dialogs-the-first-rowis-done-for-you-congratulating-expressionsresponsescongratu">
                            34. Task 5:Complete the following table with the expressions of congratulationsand the responses you find in the preceding dialogs. The first rowis done for you.Congratulating ExpressionsResponsesCongratulations! You deserved Thank you very much. Yourit, Man.support means a lot.​</h2><br />
                        <p>happy anniversary = thank you so much.</p><p>good job = thank's.</p><p>good bye, see you soon = bye, see you too.</p><p>good luck = well,thank's.</p><p>happy mothers day, mom = thank's dear.</p><p>happy holiday = happy holiday too, thank you.</p><p></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tulis-contoh-thanking-expressions-responses-and-meaning-minimal-15apologize-responses-and-meaning-minimal-15%e2%80%8b">
                            35. Tulis contoh:* Thanking expressions, responses and meaning (minimal 15)*Apologize, responses and meaning (minimal 15)​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>
</p><p>* Ucapan terima kasih, tanggapan dan makna (minimal 15)
</p><p>* Minta maaf, tanggapan dan makna (minimal 15)</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>maaf kalau salah</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="write-3-expressions-and-responses-to-congratulate%e2%80%8b">
                            36. Write 3 expressions and responses to Congratulate!​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>3 expressions</p><p></p><p>1. Ketika teman kamu mendapat Juara kelas</p><p>respon: Wow, I'm very happy because your Chaption Class</p><p></p><p>2.ketika t3manmu ulang tahun</p><p>respon: Hello, Good goob,Happy best day my friend</p><p></p><p>3.ketika Kakakmu menikah</p><p>Respon: Hello, I'm very happy and I hope they so family on very happy</p><p></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="mention-five-expressions-of-thanking-and-its-responses">
                            37. Mention five expressions of thanking and its  responses</h2><br />
                        1. Thank you so much <br />Response : Your very welcome<br /><br />2. Thank you<br />Response : Your welcome<br /><br />3. Thanks<br />Response : Okay<br /><br />4. Thanks a lot <br />Response : Don't mention it<br /><br />5. You're so kind<br />Response : It don't matter to me<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="identify-expressions-of-congratulations-and-their-responses-used-in-the-dialog-in-activity-6-write-the-expressions-in-the-table-%e2%80%a2congratulating%e2%80%a2responding%e2%80%8b">
                            38. Identify expressions of congratulations and their responses used in the dialog in Activity 6. Write the expressions in the table.•Congratulating•Responding​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p><strong>Congratulating
</strong></p>Congratulations on becoming the new manager of the human development department. You really deserve it
Your hard work has been paid off, Bondan. Congratulations
Once again, congratulations on your promotion! We hope you can be a good manager<strong>
</strong><p><strong>
</strong></p><p><strong>Responding
</strong></p>Thank you, Reyhan. I'm nothing without your support
Thanks, Lala
Thank you, everyone. I really need your cooperation to make our dreams come true<p><strong></strong></p><p>Semoga membantu</p><p></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="5-contoh-expressionsquestion-and-responses%e2%80%8b">
                            39. 5 contoh expressions/question and responses​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>Answer:
</p><p>
</p><p>
</p><p>Expression of being grateful or thanking expression is usually uttered for saying how grateful or thankful you are after receiving something you like or need and being praised for your achievement. Here are they
</p><p>
</p><p>1.Thank you for your help
</p><p>
</p><p>2. I shall be thankful for this gifts.
</p><p>
</p><p>3. I am so grateful for your help.
</p><p>
</p><p>4. Thanks for the gifts though
</p><p>
</p><p>5. I feel grateful for your help.
</p><p>
</p><p>6. I thank you for these gifts.
</p><p>
</p><p>7. Thanks a lot for your help.
</p><p>
</p><p>8. Thank you so much for your assistance.
</p><p>
</p><p>9. I shall be grateful for your kindness.
</p><p>
</p><p>10. It is my honor to express how thankful and grateful to our fellows at war.
</p><p>
</p><p>
</p><p>The response are
</p><p>
</p><p>- you're welcome.
</p><p>
</p><p>- no problem.
</p><p>
</p><p>- That's fine/ alright
</p><p>
</p><p>
</p><p>Hopefully the explanation is clear enough to say thank you.
</p><p>
</p><p>
</p><p>Kelas: SMP
</p><p>
</p><p>Mapel: English
</p><p>
</p><p>Kategori: thanking expression</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="write-two-responses-when-a-friend-give-you-congratulations-expressions%e2%80%8b">
                            40.  Write two responses when a friend give you congratulations expressions'​</h2><br />
                        <p>Jawaban:</p><p>Ungkapan yang paling tepat digunakan ketika kita diberikan ucapan selamat oleh orang lain adalah ungkapan gratitude (terima kasih)</p><p></p><p>- Thanks!</p><p>(Terima kasih)</p><p>- You've made my day</p><p>(Kau membuatku bahagia)</p><br />
                    
